{
  "info": {
    "name": "Social Network API",
    "_postman_id": "b6a1c54f-45fe-47f6-9c6b-7a3f5b5d9c0e",
    "description": "Postman collection for Social Network backend (auth + follow + profile + users + posts + comments + reactions + notifications + websocket chat + health). All JSON responses use { success, data, error }.\n\n## WebSocket Chat\nThe WebSocket endpoint (`/ws`) provides real-time chat functionality:\n- Direct messages (1-on-1)\n- Group messages\n- Typing indicators\n- Multi-device support\n- Authenticated via session cookie\n\nSee the WebSocket folder for connection and message examples.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "test",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "try {",
          "  const json = pm.response.json();",
          "  if (Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(json, \"success\")) {",
          "    pm.test(\"response has success flag\", function () {",
          "      pm.expect(json).to.have.property(\"success\");",
          "    });",
          "  }",
          "} catch (e) {",
          "  // Non-JSON response (e.g. healthz); skip envelope check",
          "}"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
